parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents, and can also affect the backup camera, navigation, and other safety features.
The failure of the brake system can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
The failure of the electrical system can cause loss of power, stalling, and accidents.
The failure of the cruise control system can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Cruise control "sticking" and failing to disengage

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause loss of power, stalling, and accidents.
symptoms: metal pieces found in the intake manifold

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioning system can cause discomfort and distraction while driving.
symptoms: Heat exiting the vents when using the air conditioner

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch system can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feeling soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticking to the floor
clutch pedal not returning to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sunroof can cause distraction, loss of control, and potential injuries to occupants from flying glass.
symptoms: glass fragments falling into the vehicle

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of engine power can cause loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries to occupants.
The failure of the jack can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities while changing a tire.
The failure of the Uconnect system can cause distractions, accidents, and potential injuries to occupants.
The failure of safety features such as SOS and Assist buttons can cause delays in emergency response, leading to potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Busy signal when pressing SOS or Assist buttons

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical fires can cause injuries, fatalities, and property damage.
The failure of the low oil warning system can cause engine damage, accidents, and potential injuries to occupants.
symptoms: No warning lights or messages for low oil

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission issues can cause loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries to occupants.
symptoms: knocking sound when shifting into reverse.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents, injuries, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: or becomes stuck in gear; the transmission surges or hesitates; the vehicle accelerates unintentionally; the gear shifter malfunctions; the vehicle is unable to shift into gear; the check engine light comes on with codes such as P1B14-00; the vehicle makes abnormal noises or vibrations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if the vehicle surges forward or accelerates without warning.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates unintentionally; the vehicle surges forward; the vehicle hesitates or stalls; the gear shifter malfunctions; the vehicle makes abnormal noises or vibrations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the electrical, engine, or powertrain systems can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents, injuries, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: or becomes stuck in gear; the transmission surges or hesitates; the vehicle accelerates unintentionally; the gear shifter malfunctions; the vehicle makes abnormal noises or vibrations; warning lights appear on the dashboard.
